<section class="nn-faq">
  <div class="nn-faq__container">
    <div class="nn-faq__left">
      <span class="nn-faq__eyebrow">Support</span>
      <h2 class="nn-faq__heading">Got<br><em>questions?</em></h2>
      <p class="nn-faq__subline">We're always happy to help.</p>
      <a href="mailto:kirstyn@naunau.co.za" class="nn-faq__email">kirstyn@naunau.co.za</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nn-faq__right">
      <div class="nn-faq__item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="nn-faq__question" data-faq-toggle>
          <span>Are the bags really oven-safe?</span>
          <span class="nn-faq__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="nn-faq__answer" data-faq-answer>
          <div class="nn-faq__answer-inner">
            <p>Yes, safe for oven, dishwasher, fridge, freezer, microwave, and air fryer. Handles &minus;40&deg;C to 220&deg;C. Do not let the bag touch a direct heating element or open flame.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nn-faq__item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="nn-faq__question" data-faq-toggle>
          <span>How do I clean them?</span>
          <span class="nn-faq__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="nn-faq__answer" data-faq-answer>
          <div class="nn-faq__answer-inner">
            <p>Hot soapy water, leave open to air dry. Dishwasher safe (top rack). For oily residue, warm soapy water works well.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nn-faq__item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="nn-faq__question" data-faq-toggle>
          <span>What is your return policy?</span>
          <span class="nn-faq__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="nn-faq__answer" data-faq-answer>
          <div class="nn-faq__answer-inner">
            <p>30-day return policy. Unused, original condition. Contact us to arrange.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nn-faq__item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="nn-faq__question" data-faq-toggle>
          <span>How much does shipping cost?</span>
          <span class="nn-faq__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="nn-faq__answer" data-faq-answer>
          <div class="nn-faq__answer-inner">
            <p>R75 flat rate, free over R500. Ships via The Courier Guy, 3&ndash;5 business days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nn-faq__item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="nn-faq__question" data-faq-toggle>
          <span>Are they safe for kids and babies?</span>
          <span class="nn-faq__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="nn-faq__answer" data-faq-answer>
          <div class="nn-faq__answer-inner">
            <p>100% BPA-free and PVC-free. Food-grade silicone. Safe for lunchboxes, baby food, and sterilising baby products.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nn-faq__item" data-faq-item>
        <button class="nn-faq__question" data-faq-toggle>
          <span>What can I use the bags for?</span>
          <span class="nn-faq__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="nn-faq__answer" data-faq-answer>
          <div class="nn-faq__answer-inner">
            <p>Meal prep, marinating, freezing, snacks, school lunches, sous vide, travel toiletries, and more.</p>
            <a href="#ideas" class="nn-faq__ideas-link">See more ideas for your bags &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .nn-faq {
    background: #FAF7F2;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }
  .nn-faq__container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .nn-faq__left {
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }
  .nn-faq__eyebrow {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #9A8F7E;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .nn-faq__heading {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #30493B;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }
  .nn-faq__heading em {
    color: #731A47;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .nn-faq__subline {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #3D3D3D;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .nn-faq__email {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #731A47;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .nn-faq__email:hover {
    color: #30493B;
  }

  /* Accordion */
  .nn-faq__item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E0DCD5;
  }
  .nn-faq__item:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid #E0DCD5;
  }
  .nn-faq__question {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #30493B;
    text-align: left;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .nn-faq__question:hover {
    color: #731A47;
  }
  .nn-faq__icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #9A8F7E;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .nn-faq__item.is-open .nn-faq__icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    color: #731A47;
  }
  .nn-faq__answer {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease;
  }
  .nn-faq__item.is-open .nn-faq__answer {
    max-height: 300px;
  }
  .nn-faq__answer-inner {
    padding: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
  }
  .nn-faq__answer-inner p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #3D3D3D;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .nn-faq__ideas-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #731A47;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .nn-faq__ideas-link:hover {
    color: #30493B;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nn-faq { padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }
    .nn-faq__container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    .nn-faq__left {
      position: static;
    }
    .nn-faq__heading { font-size: 2.25rem; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
    const items = document.querySelectorAll('[data-faq-item]');
    items.forEach(function (item) {
      const toggle = item.querySelector('[data-faq-toggle]');
      toggle.addEventListener('click', function () {
        const isOpen = item.classList.contains('is-open');
        // Close all
        items.forEach(function (i) {
          i.classList.remove('is-open');
        });
        // Open clicked if it was closed
        if (!isOpen) {
          item.classList.add('is-open');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>

